#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:55 index.docbook:62
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-plasmapa; provides the user with a mechanism to control the volume of "
"devices and applications using the PulseAudio sound system."
msgstr ""
"&i18n-plasmapa; zagotavlja uporabniku mehanizem, s katerim lahko nadzira "
"glasnost naprav in aplikacij, z uporabo PulseAudio ozvočenja."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:60
#, no-c-format
msgid "System Settings Module"
msgstr "Modul Sistemskih Nastavitev"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-plasmapa; allows the user to control the volume of output devices, "
"application-level channels, input and recording devices. It allows the user "
"to route audio to and from specific devices. &i18n-plasmapa; consists of a "
"system settings module and a Plasma widget, which can usually be found in "
"the system tray area."
msgstr ""
"&i18n-plasmapa; omogoča uporabniku nadzor glasnosti izhodnih naprav, kanalov "
"na aplikacijski plasti, vhodnih in snemalnih naprav. Uporabniku omogoča "
"usmerjanje zvoka v in izven določenih naprav. &i18n-plasmapa; je sestavljena "
"iz modula sistemskih nastavitev in gradnika Plasme, ki se ponavadi nahaja na "
"območju sistemskega pladnja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-plasmapa; groups volume and sound settings for different channels or "
"devices into the following groups:"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-plasmapa; uredi nastavitve za glasnost in zvok za različne kanale ali "
"naprave v naslednje skupine:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Applications: Applications that play audio, such as your music player or web "
"browser."
msgstr ""
"Aplikacije: Aplikacije, ki predvajajo zvok, kot so glasbeni predvajalnik ali "
"spletni brskalnik."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Recording: Change the volume of recording devices, such as a connected "
"microphone or head set."
msgstr ""
"Snemanje: Spremeni glasnost snemalnih naprav, kot so priključen mikrofon ali "
"slušalke."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Output Devices: Output devices, you can find your headphone jack or bass "
"woofer or connected bluetooth speaker here, grouped under the sound card "
"they are connected to."
msgstr ""
"Izhodne naprave: Izhodne naprave, tu lahko najdete svoj priključek za "
"slušalke, woofer ali priključeni bluetooth zvočnik, združene pod zvočno "
"kartico, na katero so povezani."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Input Devices: Sound input devices that maybe be connected to your computer."
msgstr ""
"Vhodne Naprave: Zvočne vhodne naprave, ki so morda povezane z vašim "
"računalnikom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Configuration: This tab allows to set specific profiles to such as Analog "
"Stereo or Digital Surround 5.1. For bluetooth devices, you can switch to the "
"high-fidelity AD2P bluetooth profile here."
msgstr ""
"Konfiguracija: Ta zavihek omogoča nastavitev specifičnih profilov na takšne, "
"kot so Analog Stereo ali Digital Surrond 5.1. Za naprave z bluetooth-om "
"lahko preklopite na visoko kakovosten AD2P bluetooth profil tukaj."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:95
#, no-c-format
msgid "Plasma Widget"
msgstr "Gradnik Plasma"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &i18n-plasmapa; Plasma Widget is automatically loaded in the system tray "
"area. Clicking on the speaker icon in the panel opens a popup with volume "
"control sliders for different playback devices, and allows to change their "
"volume individually."
msgstr ""
"&i18n-plasmapa; Gradnik Plasma se samodejno naloži na sistemski pladenj. S "
"klikom na ikono zvočnika na plošči se odpre pojavno okno z drsniki za nadzor "
"glasnosti za različne naprave za predvajanje in omogoča individualno "
"spreminjanje njihove glasnosti."

